Title: Young communicator of peace and respect
DateModified: '2019-02-08'
DatePublished: '2019-02-08'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/young-communicator-of-peace-and-respect
SetInCountry: Brazil
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: "Jo\xE3o Vitor Silva  Santos"
AuthorCountry: Brazil
Text: All this begins when a young adventurer and curious wants to go in search of
  knowing new things and to live extraordinary experiences, then, he allowed himself
  to dream. In this dream, he would travel to a country, Portugal, which has the same
  language as his country, Brazil, but in this other country wonderful things awaits
  him, because through his ability to develop writings will enable him to reach hearts,
  he will sow in people the peace that the world needs so much and that respect must
  always be in the first place. To return to the country Brazil the mission does not
  for now he has become a transforming agent and is with the suitcase full to communicate
  to people that good things can happen and that it is important to fight for what
  is best for everyone, peace exists and love too.
